definitions.definition: A number of places in England :

subdefinitions.definition: A hamlet and civil parish (without a council) in Buckinghamshire , previously in Aylesbury Vale district ( OS grid ref SP6918 ) .
A suburb in Burtonwood and Westbrook parish, Warrington borough , Cheshire ( OS grid ref SJ5790 ) .
A northern suburb of Kingston upon Hull , East Riding of Yorkshire ( OS grid ref TA0834 ) .
A suburb of Basildon , Essex ( OS grid ref TQ7087 ) .
A suburban town and civil parish with a town council in South Gloucestershire district, Gloucestershire , to the northeast of Bristol ( OS grid ref ST6573 ) .
A village and civil parish in Stroud district, Gloucestershire ( OS grid ref ST7491 ) .
A hamlet in Kington Rural parish, Herefordshire ( OS grid ref SO2954 ) .
A northern suburb of Watford , Hertfordshire ( OS grid ref TL1000 )
A village in Broomfield and Kingswood parish, Maidstone district, Kent ( OS grid ref TQ8350 ) .
A hamlet in Stogumber parish, Somerset ( OS grid ref ST1037 ) .
A village in Reigate and Banstead borough , Surrey ( OS grid ref TQ2455 ) .
A settlement in Lapworth parish, Warwick district, Warwickshire ( OS grid ref SP1871 ) .

definitions.definition: A small settlement in Perth and Kinross council area, Scotland ( OS grid ref NO0638 ) .
A locality in Forden with Leighton and Trelystan community, Powys , Wales ( OS grid ref SJ2402 ) .
A suburb of Tallaght , Dublin , Ireland ( Irish grid ref O 0829 ) .
A town in Breckinridge County , Kentucky , United States .
A suburb of Sydney in the City of Penrith , New South Wales , Australia .
A suburb of Adelaide in the City of Mitcham , South Australia .
A habitational surname from Old English .
